{"tid":1980372,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞男性打扮女藝人遭性別歧視　貼三點式反擊：我有子宮卵巢","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:30:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":45,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"38d1ed4974cee02272b4bc694b6b7a4d90c06d7a","tid":1980372,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞女藝人星狄妃（Ruby）留著短髮，加上打扮中性，有時候走進女生洗手間也會令人誤會是男生，因此性別歧視在她身上經常發生。較早前Ruby在社交網站貼上一張穿泳裝以背面示人，怎料一眾網民卻留下辱罵性的說話：「不要騙我啦，男的吧」、「人妖？」、「男星來的」、「男還女？傻傻不分清」等<br />\n<br />\n事隔數天Ruby在個人Facebook專頁中，貼上一張穿三點式的泳裝正面照片，再加上長文反擊一眾歧視她性別的人，她說：「我是女生，我有胸部，有女生的器官，有子宮有卵巢，每個月也會有大姨媽報到。我是女生，但我平日喜歡中性打扮。我是女生，但是我留著一頭短髮 。我是女生，但朋友們都認為我體內住著所謂『男人的靈魂』。我是女生，但我平日看起來就像個男的，進女廁所也會被人看多兩眼。所以呢？是誰規定女生就一定要長髮穿裙子。」<br />\n<br />\nRuby認為中性打扮並不代表她是想成為男人，只是想以覺最舒服的狀態示人。她直言這篇長文只是針對那些愛諷刺的人；「至少我對人說話懂得什麼叫尊重而你不懂，很抱歉，或許會讓部分人感覺不舒服。本來還在想要不要發這照片，但讀了新聞的留言以後，實在忍不住了。這是我第一次這麼直白的在這裡發洩我的不平衡，但別誤會，我沒有生氣。寫的時候是心平氣和的 ，沒有美化詞句，敬請體諒。最後，希望大家可以學會尊重人，不管是男性女性，都應該被尊重。人家管不到你的嘴和手，那你也別管人家的生活，祝福大家都能做最舒服自在的自己。」"},{"pid":"08779e72a174a680a9d85ba0b9f2ac8efd741b1d","tid":1980372,"uid":16659,"like":29,"dislike":27,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4349701/org/548b65ae004d17ecaaff683918c72484.jpg/GmGKddynbd0lsOyd6IZ9QPCvSAO1FkzqFlOP5RZTj-U?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4349701%2Forg%2F548b65ae004d17ecaaff683918c72484.jpg%2FGmGKddynbd0lsOyd6IZ9QPCvSAO1FkzqFlOP5RZTj-U%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=68b83b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前Ruby罕有Facebook post泳裝照。（Facebook：Ruby 狄妃）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4349704/org/f12c43b5aef181e2655cff448ce5cc3e.jpg/7uKe5SnqSDtL-UGdQPj9qDZpstxXcFbEyZaOrMmWjqw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4349704%2Forg%2Ff12c43b5aef181e2655cff448ce5cc3e.jpg%2F7uKe5SnqSDtL-UGdQPj9qDZpstxXcFbEyZaOrMmWjqw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=506c4c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRuby以長文反擊一眾性別歧視她的人。（Facebook：Ruby 狄妃）"},{"pid":"a8f89f2492f145a67df1ce16d4d307b27ffc77b4","tid":1980372,"uid":16659,"like":21,"dislike":37,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4349997/org/13084c2e4d04206718714ee41a940fdb.jpg/43a9ovjn_hMtSgRcKzdfGsp6mkOZ-YLjuc_kErnP5BI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4349997%2Forg%2F13084c2e4d04206718714ee41a940fdb.jpg%2F43a9ovjn_hMtSgRcKzdfGsp6mkOZ-YLjuc_kErnP5BI&h=8cc70bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4350006/org/961a5f232ae367bd0e488795d2fd880e.jpg/U_9sHnxbM6OXtlrPygDOXLwKNJ9Iga7iaRM_GGkTPxg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4350006%2Forg%2F961a5f232ae367bd0e488795d2fd880e.jpg%2FU_9sHnxbM6OXtlrPygDOXLwKNJ9Iga7iaRM_GGkTPxg&h=bb624dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4350010/org/f55fd6acbd6b99747566a7275dc82476.jpg/swYuTKL1iBZ0bdf4q5nodbUwyxxnRkJ6FgRtjBYEbYw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4350010%2Forg%2Ff55fd6acbd6b99747566a7275dc82476.jpg%2FswYuTKL1iBZ0bdf4q5nodbUwyxxnRkJ6FgRtjBYEbYw&h=20c3a08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4350001/org/9a04bd12fdbe43fbfc05299032b67fd2.jpg/F52_UIp6BqH5Hx7KTxZwfnx5V7NPLPjar3h5h694eYc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4350001%2Forg%2F9a04bd12fdbe43fbfc05299032b67fd2.jpg%2FF52_UIp6BqH5Hx7KTxZwfnx5V7NPLPjar3h5h694eYc&h=2d15fb7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1635bea0720484929f057be3ffd9dc8ef75aa48c","tid":1980372,"uid":132174,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"印度佬嗰type"},{"pid":"aaa14190a5a0dfef1350abcc6ff4b9fa3b024b58","tid":1980372,"uid":229026,"like